506
00:35:08,234 --> 00:35:11,431
Naturally ! All of our dads
were these big shots.

507
00:35:11,514 --> 00:35:13,425
And Mom...

508
00:35:13,514 --> 00:35:16,392
was like... superwoman.

509
00:35:17,714 --> 00:35:21,627
