536
00:36:37,274 --> 00:36:41,347
''According to our files,
his mother did not die...

537
00:36:41,434 --> 00:36:43,231
- ''during birth.
- She's not dead.

538
00:36:43,314 --> 00:36:45,623
''We have a current
address for her at...

539
00:36:45,714 --> 00:36:47,705
''172 Canyon Glen Drive,
Los Angeles.

540
00:36:47,794 --> 00:36:50,513
