thought we were going to Hawaii.

582
00:39:04,194 --> 00:39:06,503
- The parking attendant ?
- He liked the car.

583
00:39:06,594 --> 00:39:08,983
We put on those loud shirts
so we'd look like tourists.

584
00:39:09,074 --> 00:39:12,464
You know,
I just realized that...

585
00:39:12,554 --> 00:39:15,387
in over 20 years of service,
not one of my clients...

586
00:39:15,474 --> 00:39:17,271
