a problem. Hey !

588
00:39:21,034 --> 00:39:23,468
No, please, please !

589
00:39:42,154 --> 00:39:44,907
- Hi.
- Hi.

590
00:39:44,994 --> 00:39:49,465
- Oh, excuse me, could you
tell me who lives here ?
