your little journey.

615
00:41:33,234 --> 00:41:37,147
When you get near Houston,
phone 713-555-0342...

616
00:41:37,234 --> 00:41:40,670
and ask for uh, uh,
Beetroot Mckinley.

617
00:41:40,754 --> 00:41:44,542
He will arrange to trade you a briefcase
for the merchandise in the trunk.

618
00:41:44,634 --> 00:41:46,511
Thank you.

619
00:41:46,594 --> 00:41:49,552
Mary Ann Benedict.

620
00:41:49,634 --> 00:41:54,025
I haven't said that name
out loud for over 30 years.

621
00:41:54,114 --> 00:41:56,628
Your mother was...

622
00:41:56,714 --> 00:41:58,944
an amazing woman.

623
00:41:59,034 --> 00:42:03,391
