have happened if I'd have married her.

624
00:42:03,474 --> 00:42:05,669
Why didn't you ?

625
00:42:05,754 --> 00:42:09,303
Oh, I asked her to.
She turned me down.

626
00:42:09,394 --> 00:42:12,909
She said she was afraid...

627
00:42:12,994 --> 00:42:15,428
to have any more children.

628
00:42:15,514 --> 00:42:18,392
See, they told her
you had died at birth.

629
00:42:18,474 --> 00:42:20,988
Who told her we died ?

630
00:42:25,674 --> 00:42:27,790
Mitchell Traven,
the guy with the clipboard.

631
00:42:27,874 --> 00:42:30,752
