for the government.

632
00:42:30,834 --> 00:42:35,032
He still runs a genetics lab
at Los Alamos, New Mexico.

633
00:42:35,114 --> 00:42:37,309
I'll have to pay
him a visit.

634
00:42:37,394 --> 00:42:39,544
Watch out for him.

635
00:42:39,634 --> 00:42:43,183
He's kind of a dickhead,
if you know what I mean.

636
00:42:43,274 --> 00:42:46,789
Dickhead ?

637
00:42:46,874 --> 00:42:49,308
No, I don't.

638
00:42:49,394 --> 00:42:52,466
But... I'm learning.

639
00:42:57,474 --> 00:43:00,113
- I'm concerned about the time frame.
- [ Ringing ]

640
00:43:00,194 --> 00:43:02,913
That's my private line, honey.
I'll take care of that.

641
00:43:02,994 --> 00:43:05,303
You boys, excuse me.

642
00:43:11,594 --> 00:43:13,744
Beetroot Mckinley talkin'.
