Hey, Jules. Marnie's
got the hots for you, babe.

990
01:08:11,874 --> 01:08:13,751
Tonight is your lucky night.
I know it.

991
01:08:13,834 --> 01:08:17,668
- I don't think Marnie likes me.
- You kidding ? Piece of cake.

992
01:08:17,754 --> 01:08:20,507
This woman is ripe.
You're nervous...

993
